{"type": "USJ", "version": "3.1", "content": [{"type": "book", "marker": "id", "content": ["25-LAM-web.sfm English Arabic Names Version (EANV)"], "code": "LAM"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "ide", "content": ["UTF-8\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "h", "content": ["Lamentations \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "toc1", "content": ["The Lamentations of Jeremiah \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "toc2", "content": ["Lamentations \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "toc3", "content": ["Lam \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "mt2", "content": ["The \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "mt1", "content": ["Lamentations \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "mt2", "content": ["of Jeremiah \n"]}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "1", "sid": "LAM 1"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "LAM 1:1"}, "How the city sits solitary, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["that was full of people! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["She has become as a widow, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["who was great amongst the nations! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["She who was a princess amongst the provinces \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["has become a slave! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "LAM 1:2"}, "She weeps bitterly in the night. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Her tears are on her cheeks. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Amongst all her lovers \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["she has no one to comfort her. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["All her friends have dealt treacherously with her. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They have become her enemies. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "LAM 1:3"}, "Judah has gone into captivity because of affliction, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and because of great servitude. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["She dwells amongst the nations. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["She finds no rest. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["All her persecutors overtook her within the straits. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "LAM 1:4"}, "The roads to Zion mourn, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["because no one comes to the solemn assembly. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["All her gates are desolate. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Her priests sigh. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Her virgins are afflicted, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and she herself is in bitterness. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "LAM 1:5"}, "Her adversaries have become the head. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Her enemies prosper; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["for the LORD", {"type": "note", "marker": "f", "content": ["  ", {"type": "char", "marker": "fr", "content": ["1:5 "]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "ft", "content": ["When rendered in ALL CAPITAL LETTERS, \u201cLORD\u201d or \u201cALLAH\u201d is the translation of Allah\u2019s Proper\nName."]}], "caller": "+"}, " has afflicted her for the multitude of her transgressions.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Her young children have gone into captivity before the adversary.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "LAM 1:6"}, "All majesty has departed from the daughter of Zion. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Her princes have become like deer that find no pasture. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They have gone without strength before the pursuer. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "LAM 1:7"}, "Jerusalem remembers in the days of her affliction and of her miseries\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["all her pleasant things that were from the days of old; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["when her people fell into the hand of the adversary, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and no one helped her. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["The adversaries saw her. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They mocked at her desolations. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "LAM 1:8"}, "Jerusalem has grievously sinned. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Therefore she has become unclean. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["All who honoured her despise her, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["because they have seen her nakedness. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Yes, she sighs, and turns backward. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "LAM 1:9"}, "Her filthiness was in her skirts. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["She didn\u2019t remember her latter end. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Therefore she has come down astoundingly. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["She has no comforter. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["\u201cSee, LORD, my affliction; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for the enemy has magnified himself.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "LAM 1:10"}, "The adversary has spread out his hand on all her pleasant things;\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for she has seen that the nations have entered into her sanctuary,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["concerning whom you commanded that they should not enter into your assembly.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "LAM 1:11"}, "All her people sigh. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They seek bread. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They have given their pleasant things for food to refresh their soul.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["\u201cLook, LORD, and see; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for I have become despised.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "LAM 1:12"}, "\u201cIs it nothing to you, all you who pass by? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Look, and see if there is any sorrow like my sorrow, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["which is brought on me, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["with which the LORD has afflicted me in the day of his fierce anger.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "13", "sid": "LAM 1:13"}, "\u201cFrom on high has he sent fire into my bones, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and it prevails against them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["He has spread a net for my feet. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has turned me back. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has made me desolate and I faint all day long. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "14", "sid": "LAM 1:14"}, "\u201cThe yoke of my transgressions is bound by his hand. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They are knit together. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They have come up on my neck. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He made my strength fail. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["The Lord", {"type": "note", "marker": "f", "content": ["  ", {"type": "char", "marker": "fr", "content": ["1:14 "]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "ft", "content": ["The word translated \u201cLord\u201d is \u201cAdonai.\u201d"]}], "caller": "+"}, " has delivered me into their hands,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["against whom I am not able to stand. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "15", "sid": "LAM 1:15"}, "\u201cThe Lord has set at nothing all my mighty men within me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has called a solemn assembly against me to crush my young men.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The Lord has trodden the virgin daughter of Judah as in a wine press.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "16", "sid": "LAM 1:16"}, "\u201cFor these things I weep. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["My eye, my eye runs down with water, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["because the comforter who should refresh my soul is far from me.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["My children are desolate, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["because the enemy has prevailed.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "17", "sid": "LAM 1:17"}, "Zion spreads out her hands. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["There is no one to comfort her. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["The LORD has commanded concerning Yaqub, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["that those who are around him should be his adversaries. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Jerusalem is amongst them as an unclean thing. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "18", "sid": "LAM 1:18"}, "\u201cThe LORD is righteous; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for I have rebelled against his commandment. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Please hear all you peoples, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and see my sorrow. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["My virgins and my young men have gone into captivity. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "19", "sid": "LAM 1:19"}, "\u201cI called for my lovers, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["but they deceived me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["My priests and my elders gave up the spirit in the city, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["while they sought food for themselves to refresh their souls.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "20", "sid": "LAM 1:20"}, "\u201cLook, LORD; for I am in distress. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["My heart is troubled. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["My heart turns over within me, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for I have grievously rebelled. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Abroad, the sword bereaves. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["At home, it is like death. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "21", "sid": "LAM 1:21"}, "\u201cThey have heard that I sigh. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["There is no one to comfort me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["All my enemies have heard of my trouble. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They are glad that you have done it. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["You will bring the day that you have proclaimed, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and they will be like me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "22", "sid": "LAM 1:22"}, "\u201cLet all their wickedness come before you. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Do to them as you have done to me for all my transgressions.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["For my sighs are many, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and my heart is faint. \n"]}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "2", "sid": "LAM 2"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "LAM 2:1"}, "How has the Lord covered the daughter of Zion with a cloud in his anger!\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has cast the beauty of Israel down from heaven to the earth,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and hasn\u2019t remembered his footstool in the day of his anger.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "LAM 2:2"}, "The Lord has swallowed up all the dwellings of Yaqub \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["without pity. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["He has thrown down in his wrath the strongholds of the daughter of Judah.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has brought them down to the ground. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has profaned the kingdom and its princes. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "LAM 2:3"}, "He has cut off all the horn of Israel in fierce anger. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has drawn back his right hand from before the enemy. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["He has burnt up Yaqub like a flaming fire, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["which devours all around. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "LAM 2:4"}, "He has bent his bow like an enemy. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has stood with his right hand as an adversary. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Has killed all that were pleasant to the eye. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["In the tent of the daughter of Zion, he has poured out his wrath like fire.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "LAM 2:5"}, "The Lord has become as an enemy. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has swallowed up Israel. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["He has swallowed up all her palaces. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has destroyed his strongholds. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has multiplied mourning and lamentation in the daughter of Judah.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "LAM 2:6"}, "He has violently taken away his tabernacle, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["as if it were of a garden. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["He has destroyed his place of assembly. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The LORD has caused solemn assembly and Sabbath to be forgotten in Zion.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["In the indignation of his anger, he has despised the king and the priest.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "LAM 2:7"}, "The Lord has cast off his altar. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has abhorred his sanctuary. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["He has given the walls of her palaces into the hand of the enemy.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They have made a noise in the LORD\u2019s house, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["as in the day of a solemn assembly. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "LAM 2:8"}, "The LORD has purposed to destroy the wall of the daughter of Zion.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has stretched out the line. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has not withdrawn his hand from destroying; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["He has made the rampart and wall lament. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They languish together. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "LAM 2:9"}, "Her gates have sunk into the ground. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has destroyed and broken her bars. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Her king and her princes are amongst the nations where the law is not.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Yes, her prophets find no vision from the LORD. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "LAM 2:10"}, "The elders of the daughter of Zion sit on the ground. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They keep silence. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["They have cast up dust on their heads. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They have clothed themselves with sackcloth. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The virgins of Jerusalem hang down their heads to the ground.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "LAM 2:11"}, "My eyes fail with tears. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["My heart is troubled. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["My liver is poured on the earth, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["because of the destruction of the daughter of my people, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["because the young children and the infants swoon in the streets of the city.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "LAM 2:12"}, "They ask their mothers, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["\u201cWhere is grain and wine?\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["when they swoon as the wounded in the streets of the city, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["when their soul is poured out into their mothers\u2019 bosom. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "13", "sid": "LAM 2:13"}, "What shall I testify to you? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["What shall I liken to you, daughter of Jerusalem? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["What shall I compare to you, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["that I may comfort you, virgin daughter of Zion? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["For your breach is as big as the sea. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Who can heal you? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "14", "sid": "LAM 2:14"}, "Your prophets have seen false and foolish visions for you.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They have not uncovered your iniquity, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["to reverse your captivity, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["but have seen for you false revelations and causes of banishment.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "15", "sid": "LAM 2:15"}, "All that pass by clap their hands at you. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They hiss and wag their head at the daughter of Jerusalem, saying,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["\u201cIs this the city that men called \u2018The perfection of beauty,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["the joy of the whole earth\u2019?\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "16", "sid": "LAM 2:16"}, "All your enemies have opened their mouth wide against you.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They hiss and gnash their teeth. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They say, \u201cWe have swallowed her up. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Certainly this is the day that we looked for. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["We have found it. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["We have seen it.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "17", "sid": "LAM 2:17"}, "The LORD has done that which he planned. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has fulfilled his word that he commanded in the days of old.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["He has thrown down, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and has not pitied. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["He has caused the enemy to rejoice over you. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has exalted the horn of your adversaries. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "18", "sid": "LAM 2:18"}, "Their heart cried to the Lord. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["O wall of the daughter of Zion, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["let tears run down like a river day and night. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Give yourself no relief. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Don\u2019t let the your eyes rest. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "19", "sid": "LAM 2:19"}, "Arise, cry out in the night, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["at the beginning of the watches! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Pour out your heart like water before the face of the Lord. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Lift up your hands towards him for the life of your young children,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["who faint for hunger at the head of every street. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "20", "sid": "LAM 2:20"}, "\u201cLook, LORD, and see to whom you have done thus! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Should the women eat their offspring, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["the children that they held and bounced on their knees? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Should the priest and the prophet be killed in the sanctuary of the Lord?\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "21", "sid": "LAM 2:21"}, "\u201cThe youth and the old man lie on the ground in the streets.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["My virgins and my young men have fallen by the sword. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["You have killed them in the day of your anger. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["You have slaughtered, and not pitied. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "22", "sid": "LAM 2:22"}, "\u201cYou have called, as in the day of a solemn assembly, my terrors on every side.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["There was no one that escaped or remained in the day of the LORD\u2019s anger.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["My enemy has consumed those whom I have cared for and brought up.\n"]}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "3", "sid": "LAM 3"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "LAM 3:1"}, "I am the man who has seen affliction \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["by the rod of his wrath. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "LAM 3:2"}, "He has led me and caused me to walk in darkness, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and not in light. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "LAM 3:3"}, "Surely he turns his hand against me \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["again and again all day long. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "LAM 3:4"}, "He has made my flesh and my skin old. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has broken my bones. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "LAM 3:5"}, "He has built against me, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and surrounded me with bitterness and hardship. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "LAM 3:6"}, "He has made me dwell in dark places, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["as those who have been long dead. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "LAM 3:7"}, "He has walled me about, so that I can\u2019t go out. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has made my chain heavy. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "LAM 3:8"}, "Yes, when I cry, and call for help, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["he shuts out my prayer. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "LAM 3:9"}, "He has walled up my ways with cut stone. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has made my paths crooked. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "LAM 3:10"}, "He is to me as a bear lying in wait, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["as a lion in secret places. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "LAM 3:11"}, "He has turned away my ways, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and pulled me in pieces. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has made me desolate. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "LAM 3:12"}, "He has bent his bow, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and set me as a mark for the arrow. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "13", "sid": "LAM 3:13"}, "He has caused the shafts of his quiver to enter into my kidneys.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "14", "sid": "LAM 3:14"}, "I have become a derision to all my people, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and their song all day long. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "15", "sid": "LAM 3:15"}, "He has filled me with bitterness. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has stuffed me with wormwood. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "16", "sid": "LAM 3:16"}, "He has also broken my teeth with gravel. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has covered me with ashes. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "17", "sid": "LAM 3:17"}, "You have removed my soul far away from peace. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I forgot prosperity. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "18", "sid": "LAM 3:18"}, "I said, \u201cMy strength has perished, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["along with my expectation from the LORD.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "19", "sid": "LAM 3:19"}, "Remember my affliction and my misery, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["the wormwood and the bitterness. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "20", "sid": "LAM 3:20"}, "My soul still remembers them, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and is bowed down within me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "21", "sid": "LAM 3:21"}, "This I recall to my mind; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["therefore I have hope. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "22", "sid": "LAM 3:22"}, "It is because of The LORD\u2019s loving kindnesses that we are not consumed,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["because his compassion doesn\u2019t fail. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "23", "sid": "LAM 3:23"}, "They are new every morning. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Great is your faithfulness. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "24", "sid": "LAM 3:24"}, "\u201cThe LORD is my portion,\u201d says my soul. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["\u201cTherefore I will hope in him.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "25", "sid": "LAM 3:25"}, "The LORD is good to those who wait for him, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["to the soul who seeks him. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "26", "sid": "LAM 3:26"}, "It is good that a man should hope \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and quietly wait for the salvation of the LORD. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "27", "sid": "LAM 3:27"}, "It is good for a man that he bear the yoke in his youth. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "28", "sid": "LAM 3:28"}, "Let him sit alone and keep silence, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["because he has laid it on him. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "29", "sid": "LAM 3:29"}, "Let him put his mouth in the dust, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["if it is so that there may be hope. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "30", "sid": "LAM 3:30"}, "Let him give his cheek to him who strikes him. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Let him be filled full of reproach. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "31", "sid": "LAM 3:31"}, "For the Lord will not cast off forever. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "32", "sid": "LAM 3:32"}, "For though he causes grief, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["yet he will have compassion according to the multitude of his loving kindnesses.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "33", "sid": "LAM 3:33"}, "For he does not afflict willingly, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["nor grieve the children of men. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "34", "sid": "LAM 3:34"}, "To crush under foot all the prisoners of the earth, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "35", "sid": "LAM 3:35"}, "to turn away the right of a man before the face of the Most High,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "36", "sid": "LAM 3:36"}, "to subvert a man in his cause, the Lord doesn\u2019t approve. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "37", "sid": "LAM 3:37"}, "Who is he who says, and it comes to pass, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["when the Lord doesn\u2019t command it? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "38", "sid": "LAM 3:38"}, "Doesn\u2019t evil and good come out of the mouth of the Most High?\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "39", "sid": "LAM 3:39"}, "Why does a living man complain, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["a man for the punishment of his sins? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "40", "sid": "LAM 3:40"}, "Let us search and try our ways, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and turn again to the LORD. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "41", "sid": "LAM 3:41"}, "Let\u2019s lift up our heart with our hands to Allah", {"type": "note", "marker": "f", "content": ["  ", {"type": "char", "marker": "fr", "content": ["3:41\n"]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "ft", "content": ["The Hebrew word rendered \u201cAllah\u201d is \u201c\u05d0\u05b1\u05dc\u05b9\u05d4\u05b4\u0591\u05d9\u05dd\u201d (Elohim)."]}], "caller": "+"}, " in the heavens.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "42", "sid": "LAM 3:42"}, "\u201cWe have transgressed and have rebelled. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["You have not pardoned. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "43", "sid": "LAM 3:43"}, "\u201cYou have covered us with anger and pursued us. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["You have killed. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["You have not pitied. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "44", "sid": "LAM 3:44"}, "You have covered yourself with a cloud, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["so that no prayer can pass through. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "45", "sid": "LAM 3:45"}, "You have made us an off-scouring and refuse \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["in the middle of the peoples. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "46", "sid": "LAM 3:46"}, "\u201cAll our enemies have opened their mouth wide against us. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "47", "sid": "LAM 3:47"}, "Terror and the pit have come on us, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["devastation and destruction.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "48", "sid": "LAM 3:48"}, "My eye runs down with streams of water, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for the destruction of the daughter of my people. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "49", "sid": "LAM 3:49"}, "My eye pours down \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and doesn\u2019t cease, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["without any intermission, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "50", "sid": "LAM 3:50"}, "until the LORD looks down, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and sees from heaven. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "51", "sid": "LAM 3:51"}, "My eye affects my soul, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["because of all the daughters of my city. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "52", "sid": "LAM 3:52"}, "They have chased me relentlessly like a bird, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["those who are my enemies without cause. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "53", "sid": "LAM 3:53"}, "They have cut off my life in the dungeon, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and have cast a stone on me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "54", "sid": "LAM 3:54"}, "Waters flowed over my head. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I said, \u201cI am cut off.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "55", "sid": "LAM 3:55"}, "I called on your name, LORD, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["out of the lowest dungeon. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "56", "sid": "LAM 3:56"}, "You heard my voice: \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["\u201cDon\u2019t hide your ear from my sighing, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and my cry.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "57", "sid": "LAM 3:57"}, "You came near in the day that I called on you. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["You said, \u201cDon\u2019t be afraid.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "58", "sid": "LAM 3:58"}, "Lord, you have pleaded the causes of my soul. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["You have redeemed my life. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "59", "sid": "LAM 3:59"}, "LORD, you have seen my wrong. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Judge my cause. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "60", "sid": "LAM 3:60"}, "You have seen all their vengeance \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and all their plans against me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "61", "sid": "LAM 3:61"}, "You have heard their reproach, LORD, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and all their plans against me, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "62", "sid": "LAM 3:62"}, "the lips of those that rose up against me, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and their plots against me all day long. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "63", "sid": "LAM 3:63"}, "You see their sitting down and their rising up. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I am their song. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "64", "sid": "LAM 3:64"}, "You will pay them back, LORD, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["according to the work of their hands. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "65", "sid": "LAM 3:65"}, "You will give them hardness of heart, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["your curse to them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "66", "sid": "LAM 3:66"}, "You will pursue them in anger, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and destroy them from under the heavens of the LORD. \n"]}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "4", "sid": "LAM 4"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "LAM 4:1"}, "How the gold has become dim! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The most pure gold has changed! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["The stones of the sanctuary are poured out \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["at the head of every street. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "LAM 4:2"}, "The precious sons of Zion, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["comparable to fine gold, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["how they are esteemed as earthen pitchers, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["the work of the hands of the potter! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "LAM 4:3"}, "Even the jackals offer their breast. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They nurse their young ones. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["But the daughter of my people has become cruel, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["like the ostriches in the wilderness. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "LAM 4:4"}, "The tongue of the nursing child clings to the roof of his mouth for thirst.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The young children ask bread, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and no one breaks it for them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "LAM 4:5"}, "Those who ate delicacies are desolate in the streets. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Those who were brought up in purple embrace dunghills. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "LAM 4:6"}, "For the iniquity of the daughter of my people is greater than the sin of Sodom,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["which was overthrown as in a moment. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["No hands were laid on her. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "LAM 4:7"}, "Her nobles were purer than snow. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They were whiter than milk. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["They were more ruddy in body than rubies. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Their polishing was like sapphire. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "LAM 4:8"}, "Their appearance is blacker than a coal. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They are not known in the streets. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Their skin clings to their bones. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["It is withered. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["It has become like a stick. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "LAM 4:9"}, "Those who are killed with the sword are better than those who are killed with hunger;\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["For these pine away, stricken through, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for lack of the fruits of the field. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "LAM 4:10"}, "The hands of the pitiful women have boiled their own children.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They were their food in the destruction of the daughter of my people.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "LAM 4:11"}, "The LORD has accomplished his wrath. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has poured out his fierce anger. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["He has kindled a fire in Zion, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["which has devoured its foundations. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "LAM 4:12"}, "The kings of the earth didn\u2019t believe, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["neither did all the inhabitants of the world, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["that the adversary and the enemy would enter into the gates of Jerusalem.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "13", "sid": "LAM 4:13"}, "It is because of the sins of her prophets \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and the iniquities of her priests, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["That have shed the blood of the just in the middle of her. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "14", "sid": "LAM 4:14"}, "They wander as blind men in the streets. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They are polluted with blood, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["So that men can\u2019t touch their garments. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "15", "sid": "LAM 4:15"}, "\u201cGo away!\u201d they cried to them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["\u201cUnclean! Go away! Go away! Don\u2019t touch! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["When they fled away and wandered, men said amongst the nations,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["\u201cThey can\u2019t live here any more.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "16", "sid": "LAM 4:16"}, "The LORD\u2019s anger has scattered them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He will not pay attention to them any more. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["They didn\u2019t respect the persons of the priests. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They didn\u2019t favour the elders. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "17", "sid": "LAM 4:17"}, "Our eyes still fail, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["looking in vain for our help. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["In our watching we have watched for a nation that could not save.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "18", "sid": "LAM 4:18"}, "They hunt our steps, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["so that we can\u2019t go in our streets. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Our end is near. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Our days are fulfilled, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for our end has come. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "19", "sid": "LAM 4:19"}, "Our pursuers were swifter than the eagles of the sky. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They chased us on the mountains. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They set an ambush for us in the wilderness. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "20", "sid": "LAM 4:20"}, "The breath of our nostrils, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["the anointed of the LORD, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["was taken in their pits; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["of whom we said, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["under his shadow we will live amongst the nations. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "21", "sid": "LAM 4:21"}, "Rejoice and be glad, daughter of Edom, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["that dwells in the land of Uz. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["The cup will pass through to you also. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["You will be drunken, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and will make yourself naked. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "22", "sid": "LAM 4:22"}, "The punishment of your iniquity is accomplished, daughter of Zion.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He will no more carry you away into captivity. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["He will visit your iniquity, daughter of Edom. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He will uncover your sins. \n"]}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "5", "sid": "LAM 5"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "LAM 5:1"}, "Remember, LORD, what has come on us. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Look, and see our reproach. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "LAM 5:2"}, "Our inheritance has been turned over to strangers, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["our houses to aliens. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "LAM 5:3"}, "We are orphans and fatherless. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Our mothers are as widows. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "LAM 5:4"}, "We have drunken our water for money. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Our wood is sold to us. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "LAM 5:5"}, "Our pursuers are on our necks. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["We are weary, and have no rest. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "LAM 5:6"}, "We have given our hands to the Egyptians, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and to the Assyrians, to be satisfied with bread. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "LAM 5:7"}, "Our fathers sinned, and are no more. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["We have borne their iniquities. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "LAM 5:8"}, "Servants rule over us. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["There is no one to deliver us out of their hand. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "LAM 5:9"}, "We get our bread at the peril of our lives, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["because of the sword of the wilderness. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "LAM 5:10"}, "Our skin is black like an oven, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["because of the burning heat of famine. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "LAM 5:11"}, "They ravished the women in Zion, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["the virgins in the cities of Judah. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "LAM 5:12"}, "Princes were hanged up by their hands. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The faces of elders were not honoured. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "13", "sid": "LAM 5:13"}, "The young men carry millstones. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The children stumbled under loads of wood. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "14", "sid": "LAM 5:14"}, "The elders have ceased from the gate, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and the young men from their music. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "15", "sid": "LAM 5:15"}, "The joy of our heart has ceased. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Our dance is turned into mourning. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "16", "sid": "LAM 5:16"}, "The crown has fallen from our head. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Woe to us, for we have sinned! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "17", "sid": "LAM 5:17"}, "For this our heart is faint. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["For these things our eyes are dim. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "18", "sid": "LAM 5:18"}, "For the mountain of Zion, which is desolate. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The foxes walk on it. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "19", "sid": "LAM 5:19"}, "You, LORD, remain forever. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Your throne is from generation to generation. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "20", "sid": "LAM 5:20"}, "Why do you forget us forever, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and forsake us for so long a time? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "21", "sid": "LAM 5:21"}, "Turn us to yourself, LORD, and we will be turned. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Renew our days as of old. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "22", "sid": "LAM 5:22"}, "But you have utterly rejected us. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["You are very angry against us. "]}]}